{"tid":1132910,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"窮婦人祖記又要免簽馬達了","createTime":"2019-04-30T15:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T03:03:27.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"39b42533e4ff3f40e9067fb19ce503b391c7b129","tid":1132910,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:53:30.000Z","msg":"直播吧4月30日訊 據《拖連奴體育報》報導，曼聯中場馬達已經在祖雲達斯今夏的收購名單上，老婦人已經向球員遞送了第一份報價。<br />\n<br />\n  馬達與曼聯的合約今年夏天即將到期，就目前看來球員不會和球會續約。今季31歲的馬達在隊內出場時間有限，一共出場31次，其中僅有20次正選，攻入6球並有2次助攻，其中就包括上輪聯賽戰平車路士的首開紀錄。"},{"pid":"14eeb5f8a88c50d9a691257027667e26c83910a5","tid":1132910,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:54:57.000Z","msg":"上年搵贊助簽到阿朗真係奇蹟"},{"pid":"45f58587b26fb6d0a31224a210a6b4dc4e776a5e","tid":1132910,"uid":133184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T17:12:51.000Z","msg":"免費汁靚貨"},{"pid":"6db265bad543c7cd08d3a2fa80e0ce3fdc251014","tid":1132910,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce438bcf9f1a0800a2510f3cd511d5b2083f071c","tid":1132910,"uid":27485,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"簽埋簽埋<br />\n係意大利就話屈機<br />\n行落銅鑼灣就收皮啦"},{"pid":"dd8752ac75ad40543eba4dc94484a7746ede40fc","tid":1132910,"uid":114217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:49:17.000Z","msg":"藍斯做馬達後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a89889b1ffece915eb7c9b4f721674a07ad335","tid":1132910,"uid":15846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce438bcf9f1a0800a2510f3cd511d5b2083f071c","tid":1132910,"uid":27485,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"簽埋簽埋<br />\n係意大利就話屈機<br />\n行落銅鑼灣就收皮啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:53:50.000Z","msg":"真，邊夠膽嚟香港大球場"},{"pid":"c0ce9caad0190045